@startuml
title "UC-08: Deliver Orders"

actor "Delivery Staff" as Delivery
participant "Mr. Daebak System" as System

== Load Delivery Orders ==
Delivery -> System: 1. Request assigned orders
activate System
System --> Delivery: 2. Order list\n(PREPARING/DELIVERING status)
deactivate System

== Start Delivery ==
Delivery -> System: 3. Update order status\n(order_id, status: DELIVERING)
activate System
System --> Delivery: 4. Status updated successfully
deactivate System

== Complete Delivery ==
Delivery -> System: 5. Update order status\n(order_id, status: COMPLETED)
activate System
System --> Delivery: 6. Delivery completed successfully
deactivate System

@enduml
